edu.umd.cs.jazz.component
Interface ZAppearance

All Known Subinterfaces:
ZFillColor, ZFillPaint, ZPenColor, ZPenPaint, ZStroke
All Known Implementing Classes:
ZBasicVisualComponent, ZCamera, ZLabel, ZText
public interface ZAppearance

ZAppearance represents a visual attribute of a visual component. This interface is just a "tag" meant to be extended by interfaces that define visual attributes.

Author:
Benjamin B. Bederson
